<br />

<br />
If you're in a situation where you're getting spells cast at you or shot at and you don't see your attacker, charm the closest humanoid to you. By default it will bee line directly towards the attacker.
<br />

<br />
.... I had a leprican cast on me and it worked so I assume this will work in RvR vs those silly bow shooters.</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
