				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Senreni, yes that was my point... We could in theory send in several mobs to wreck havoc...
<br />

<br />
As far as the exp loss question goes... you DO losse exp if you die to a mob. So I assume that if you charm a mob and send it after someone but break the charm before it kills them that you would in fact loose exp... unless they keep track of the fact the mob had been charmed recently.
<br />

<br />
Either way its still a cool tactic. The only problem is that you'd need a pretty high level charm to get it to work on the mobs in the RvR region. Everything out there is pretty high level.</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
