<br />
2) rush attack the tanks. Archers tag DD casters.
<br />
3)With no one healing the nukers they should die quickly, then archers turn to attack their healers.
<br />
4)At this point their healing tanks will have to stop tanking to try to save the healers who are left, nah, kill them next!
<br />

